paragraphs.body: Hello, my name is Annalise and I'm obsessed with cartoons. I probrobly sound like a geek but that's who I am. I can't help it! But I like other things too. I am a Swiftie (Taylor Swift lover), Rusher (Big Time Rush lover) and a fan of Justin Bieber, Katelyn Tarver, Selena Gomez, Jelena, GREY DELISLE (all the way), Monster High, Barbie, LaDeeDa and romance in general (I'm a helpless romatic). What cartoons am I obsessed with? I'll tell you. Avatar: The Last Airbender (mostly), The Legend of Korra (also mostly, lol), Danny Phantom, Fairly OddParents, T.U.F.F Puppy, The Amazing World of Gumball and MAD. The things I put in BOLD are what I'm REALLY into right now. My fave chartoon characters are... Suki (Avatar), Sam (Danny Phantom), Sokka (Avatar), Spectra Vondergeist (Monster High), Mako (Korra) and Bolin (Korra). I am also obsessed with cats and the number 13. I ship the following..
